'''-{zh-hant:單走道客機;zh-hans:窄体飞机;}-'''（-{zh-tw:{{lang-en|Single Aisle Aircraft}};zh-cn:{{lang-en|Narrow-body Aircraft}}}-），又常稱為'''-{zh-hant:窄體客機;zh-hans:单走道客机;}-'''（-{zh-hant:Narrow-body Aircraft; zh-hans:Single Aisle Aircraft;}-），一般指飞机机身直径在4米（10到13英尺）以下的飞机。而客機机舱每排座位一般能乘坐2到6名乘客。搭乘人數最多一般在50-250左右，並配置一条走道，因而得名<ref name="travelPro">{{cite book| title = A Guide to Becoming a Travel Professional| author1 = Ginger Gorham| author2 = Ginger Todd| author3 = Susan Rice| publisher = Cengage Learning| year = 2003| ISBN = 9781401851774| page = [https://archive.org/details/guidetobecomingt0000gorh/page/40 40]| url = https://archive.org/details/guidetobecomingt0000gorh/page/40}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url = http://www.businessdictionary.com/definition/narrowbody-aircraft.html|title = narrowbody aircraft|accessdate = 2009-03-18}}</ref><ref>{{cite book| page = 552| title = Flight International| author = [[Royal_Aero_Club|Royal Aero Club]] (Great Britain), Royal Aero Club of the United Kingdom| year = 1967| publisher = IPC Transport Press Ltd.| url = https://books.google.com/books?id=U3s7AAAAMAAJ&pgis=1}}</ref>。

另外，相对的也會提到[[廣體客機|廣體客機]]，廣體則是機艙斷面較窄体飞机更寬廣、且通常設置有多个舱等的中大型客機。此類機種定義是機外直径約在5到6米（16到20英尺）之間，並且配置至少两条走道，通常一排能够容纳7到10个座位。相對於通常可搭载300至800多名乘客的广体客机<ref name="travelPro"/><ref>{{cite news| url = http://select.nytimes.com/gst/abstract.html?res=F20E15F93C59107A93CBA81788D85F468785F9&scp=133&sq=wide-body&st=p| title = the traveler's world; Test of a New Wide-Bodied Airbus| author = Paul J. C. Friedlander| newspaper = New York Times| date = 1972-03-19}}</ref><ref>{{cite book| page = [https://archive.org/details/flyingoffcoursee00doga/page/n186 170]| title = Flying Off Course: The Economics of International Airlines| url = https://archive.org/details/flyingoffcoursee00doga| url-access = limited| author = Doganis, Rigas| publisher = Routledge| year = 2002| ISBN = 9780415213240}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.airbus.com/aircraftfamilies/passengeraircraft/a380family/a380-800/specifications/ |title=Dimensions & key data | Airbus, a leading aircraft manufacturer |publisher=Airbus.com |date=2012-09-27 |accessdate=2012-10-01}}</ref>。

